      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>To view the LCM status, select <uicontrol>Diagnosis</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol>LCM status</uicontrol>.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <p>When no alert is pending, the following is shown on the
display:<table>
                     <tgroup cols="1">
                        <colspec colname="col1"/>
                        <tbody>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <screen xml:space="preserve">LCM status:No alert pending</screen>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>When an alert is pending (and is only temporarily acknowledged
by a user), the actual alert is shown on the display:<table>
                     <tgroup cols="1">
                        <colspec colname="col1"/>
                        <tbody>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <screen xml:space="preserve">LCM status:Tech. check needed</screen>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>
               </p>
            </stepxmp>
